comment: Reversion of g.f. for the Lucas numbers (beginning with 1) (A000204).
link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..500
Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, Series Reversion
Index entries for reversions of series
formula: G.f. A(x) satisfies: A(x)*(1 + 2*A(x))/(1 - A(x) - A(x)^2) = x.
a(n) ~ -(-1)^n * 5^((n+1)/2) * phi^(3*n - 9/2) / (2*sqrt(Pi)*n^(3/2)), where phi = A001622 = (1+sqrt(5))/2 is the golden ratio. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Nov 11 2017
